Musio: Hi there! What's your favorite hobby?

User: I love playing video games!

Musio: That's great! What kind of video games do you like to play?

User: I really like action and adventure games. I also like puzzles and strategy games.

Musio: That sounds like a lot of fun! Do you have any favorite video games?

User: Yes, I have a few favorites. I really like the "Legend of Zelda" series, "Super Mario Bros.", and "Pokemon".

Musio: Those are all great games! I'm sure you have a lot of fun playing them.

User: Yeah, I do. I can't wait to play the new "Legend of Zelda" game that's coming out soon.